-.003(Efficiency and correctness)A
90 118 :M
f0_10 sf
-.003(Efficiency and correctness are considered together in this discussion because one of the most effective ways)A
90 138 :M
-.007(of improving efficiency in object recognition has been to permit some relaxation of the assurance of cor-)A
90 158 :M
-.008(rectness. That tactic has been responsible, in part, for the performance gains of indexing methods like geo)A
513 158 :M
(-)S
90 178 :M
-.008(metric hashing, and of matching methods like alignment. There is much more work to be done exploring)A
90 198 :M
-.006(ways that recognition can be made fast by permitting answers to be approximate or occasionally sub-)A
90 218 :M
-.007(optimal.)A
90 248 :M
-.001(Efficiency remains an important problem despite continuing improvements in computational power and)A
90 268 :M
-.004(algorithms. Recognition systems that work with large databases of complex objects still appear to be)A
90 288 :M
-.009(beyond the reach of the practicable. However, some interesting ideas have been proposed for improving)A
90 308 :M
-.007(efficiency and, although these have been tried out individually, the task now appears to be to find effective)A
90 328 :M
-.005(ways of integrating them. For matching, different strategies such as coarse-to-fine, part-to-whole, and)A
90 348 :M
-.007(abstract-to-specific have been described. Each might be best in certain situations, but the best overall)A
90 368 :M
-.006(performance may come from integrating them or choosing among them as needed.)A
90 398 :M
-.005(An object recognition system should fine-tune itself according to the contents of its model library and the)A
90 418 :M
-.004(images it is seeing. If an index table is used, for example, then the table\325s quantization level could be)A
90 438 :M
-.01(adjusted according to the number of entries it contains and the degree of accuracy found in image mea)A
499 438 :M
(-)S
90 458 :M
-.005(surements. Grouping thresholds could be adjusted according to the prevalence of those groups among)A
90 478 :M
-.004(objects and the degree of clutter found in images. Such parameters are now established statically in most)A
90 498 :M
-.007(systems, but they, and the performance of the system, could be improved through automated learning.)A
endp
